songs.title: Interlude - Highest (Part 2)
songs.lyrics:
[Suli Breaks]
There will be some that will try to deny him as saviour
Sell him out for 30 pieces of silver
These false prophets with no profit
Still too broke to even pay homage...

They will question the authenticity of his occupation
Throw dirt on his name in conversations
Buh in the end
His music
This misic
Will be the gospel for the congregation
